                        <h3>Important:</h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li>There are no right or wrong answers</li>
                            <li>Please choose based on your genuine preferences</li>
                            <li>Take your time to read and understand all information</li>
                            <li>Answer honestly and thoughtfully</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
